<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3149289" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="2"><variable id="briefum"><ahelp hid=".uno:InsertEnvelope">Creates an envelope.</ahelp> On three tab pages, you can specify the addressee and sender, the position and format for both addresses, the size of the envelope, and the envelope orientation. 
</variable></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3145416" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="E" localize="false"><link href="text/swriter/00/00000404.xhp#briefumschlag"><embedvar href="text/swriter/00/00000004.xhp#wie"/></link></paragraph>
